- Use SafeAreaView to handle notches and home indicators
- Implement SafeAreaProvider at the root of your app
- Use useSafeAreaInsets hook for dynamic safe area handling
- Ensure consistent UI across different devices and OS versions
- Consider safe areas in your layout design from the start
